{"tid":717041,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"嘈吵環鏡下 其實點解會突然靜左一秒","createTime":"2018-06-25T18:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T00:30:26.000Z","uid":168784,"like":43,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"22496d0026fd86e49d5db37b09c6e14bb94a6de9","tid":717041,"uid":168784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:36:50.000Z","msg":"應該好多巴打同絲打都試過 可能讀書班房好嘈 <br />\n突然之間靜左一下 之後又繼續嘈番<br />\n又或者餐廳食飯 個個講野嘈到飛起 <br />\n但突然又會靜左一秒<br />\n雖然唔係成日有 但一定經歷過 <br />\n但講緊係30-40個人同時無講野 其實係咩現像黎"},{"pid":"02a9c86f715cecffcea20a7a4e8ca47026ca9c0a","tid":717041,"uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:37:54.000Z","msg":"生物本能"},{"pid":"2bd6bdaf144877be3b21655304198ded1c7c05a2","tid":717041,"uid":143752,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:38:01.000Z","msg":"多數中學班房出現呢個情況"},{"pid":"534aca49b814400394f42bf9df9585cc98d2c43e","tid":717041,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:38:30.000Z","msg":"突然間大家覺得好嘈掛<br />\n以前讀書班房經常發生"},{"pid":"5f6f584f031a427920336670cb5a952d79891718","tid":717041,"uid":60695,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:39:26.000Z","msg":"寂靜星人"},{"pid":"11c2f8335e736db33143ee6e3543c1f82b38269d","tid":717041,"uid":127120,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:39:47.000Z","msg":"聽過細過話一靜係有隻天使經過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54d711ae053bb290fafd87795790cf48c805a41","tid":717041,"uid":97451,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:42:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47c13a5967febd50c31cf7bba3f766e5341d6c4f","tid":717041,"uid":41737,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T18:43:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aab4da317576195fe9dc513919c029391c3eba01","tid":717041,"uid":14914,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"47c13a5967febd50c31cf7bba3f766e5341d6c4f","ti